snippet.title: BBirthday Visual Novel - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2224400/BBirthday__Visual_Novel/
AppStore: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/bbirthday/id1610690328
PlayStore: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.LuminatheStudios.BBirthday&hl=es&gl=US
itch.io: https://yun-seven.itch.io/bbirthday

Help Bianca to relive the 15 years of her life, but from another perspective 👁️. Enjoy this dreamcore style visual novel with escape room elements and hints of horror. Unlock different endings. ✨
